  Module::Build is no longer part of core Perl and has been moved to dev-perl

  12 Mar 2015; Michael Sterrett <mr_bones_@gentoo.org> -xgamer-0.3.0.ebuild:
  old

  21 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xgamer-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #539188

  10 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xgamer-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #539188

  07 Feb 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> xgamer-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #539188

  27 Nov 2014; Andreas K. Huettel <dilfridge@gentoo.org> xgamer-0.6.2.ebuild:
  Remove call to perl-module_pkg_postinst, does not do anything outside
  perl-core

  09 Aug 2014; Mikle Kolyada <zlogene@gentoo.org> xgamer-0.3.0.ebuild:
  Bump to EAPI=5 (bug #478714)

